# BuildKit uses this (Dockerfile-adjacent) ignore file for the runtimed image
# build, whose context is the projects root (contains harness/ and runtime/).
# Exclude everything, then re-include only the two trees the Dockerfile COPYs.
*
!harness/
!runtime/

# Within the two trees, drop heavy/irrelevant artifacts.
**/.git
**/node_modules
**/.venv
**/__pycache__
**/.pytest_cache
**/dist
**/build
**/*.log
runtime/deploy/compose/.env
